        <p class="TableTextSmall">The frequency at which Pulse will run message archive task. When messages reach the age defined in the Message Archive Task Max Message Age in Day field, Pulse archives the messages and they will not display any longer in the user's task pane. 0=off, 1=1 day, 2=2days, etc.</p>
